<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> بابُ الاغْتِسَالِ لِلْمُحْرِمِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> يَدْخُلُ المُحْرِمُ الحَمَّامَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَمْ يَرَ ابْنُ عُمَرَ وَعائِشَةُ بِالحَكِّ بَأسًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>